tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"間酒樓無拉尺狗嘅？"},{"pid":"8f94f42b520510b5c117185c2ee2908fe71be325","tid":1969391,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85be96a8bff99a61a8ed0a582f5e6f0b428eca1e","tid":1969391,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"香港人忽然咁健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"個個諗住行山果陣唔洗帶口罩，於是就走晒去行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d99de1336a3a8c68b69a6b3b0f0ea8932da332","tid":1969391,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"495dec9bcbae5044ecfe06bd613618bb53b83335","tid":1969391,"uid":32620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200412/large/1586692980_e2d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200412%2Flarge%2F1586692980_e2d5.png&h=adb73e3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bf52544f486bf9b60b8c722ba4e6a24e181c5bb","tid":1969391,"uid":32620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495dec9bcbae5044ecfe06bd613618bb53b83335","tid":1969391,"uid":32620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200412/large/1586692980_e2d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200412%2Flarge%2F1586692980_e2d5.png&h=adb73e3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3ebHwbj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ebHwbj&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=1ea4a357\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3ebHwbj</a>"}]}